     {q:"Why is structure important in a formal letter or professional email?", options:["Structure has no effect on how clearly a message communicates","This element only matters in casual writing","Formal letters should have no discernible structure at all","A clear structure helps the reader follow the message’s purpose and key points"], answer:3}
